Interface Vector2D

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, CloneableSerializable, java.lang.Iterable<VectorEntry>, Pair<java.lang.Double,java.lang.Double>, Ring<Vector>, java.io.Serializable, Vector, Vectorizable, VectorSpace<Vector,VectorEntry>
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface Vector2D
extends Vector, Pair<java.lang.Double,java.lang.Double>
    An interface for a 2-dimensional vector. Adds convenience methods for accessing the two values (x, y).
